import styles from "./Registration.module.scss";

import React from "react";

function Registration({}) {
  return (
    <>

          class="text"
          type="text"
          name="Name"
          placeholder="Имя"
          required=""
        />
        <input
          class="text"
          type="text"
          name="LastName"
          placeholder="Фамилия"
          required=""
        />
        <input
          class="text"
          type="text"
          name="Patronymic"
          placeholder="Отчество (при наличии)"
          required=""
        />
        <input
          class="text"
          type="text"
          name="Email"
          placeholder="Email"
          required=""
        />
        <input
          class="text"
          type="text"
          name="localityShipping"
          placeholder="Город"
          required=""
        />
        <input
          class="text"
          type="text"
          name="addressShipping"
          placeholder="Адрес"
          required=""
        />
        <input
          class="text"
          type="text"
          name="postcode"
          placeholder="Email"
          required=""
        />
      </form>
    </>
  );
}
export default Registration;
